Plot.
A strange and powerful creature with the appearance of a man (Colm Feore) 
has come to the small town of Little Tall Island, Maine during the heaviest 
snow storm in the last 100 years. He brings with him the darkest secrets of 
all the townspeople and uses his knowledge to control and drive some of 
them to suicide and murder. But with every event, he leaves the clear 
message "Give me what I want and I'll go away." But first, he has to 
convince everyone that he has the power to destroy the village, if they 
don't comply.
